casebody.data:
Norman LAINEZ, Appellant,
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee. No. 3D18-1949 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. Opinion filed April 10, 2019 Norman Lainez, in proper person. Ashley Moody, Attorney General, and Magaly Rodriguez, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee. Before FERNANDEZ, SCALES, and LINDSEY, JJ. PER CURIAM.

We affirm and write only to commend the trial judge on his thorough and detailed order denying defendant's motion for post-conviction relief entered below.

Affirmed.
